{"tid":2286414,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解黑警咁撚諷刺","createTime":"2020-11-15T04:00:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-15T13:19:47.000Z","uid":90520,"like":461,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":79,"replies":[{"pid":"e91bafafb325abc33e9cdb81849b02360f9e00f2","tid":2286414,"uid":90520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T04:00:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E2QbXPz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE2QbXPz.png&h=c07b4e36&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sPOH4uA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsPOH4uA.png&h=a7c0aba9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一名29歲姓黃男子昨日被捕，涉嫌於灣仔警察總部內盜竊，灣仔警區重案組正調查案件。據悉，該名男子為警察公共關係科（PPRB）高級督察。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，涉案警員涉於今年8月至10月，在警察辦公室內偷走財物，包括頭盔手套等行動裝備、相機電池及罐頭鮑魚。目前涉案警員仍被扣查。警方強調會嚴正處理事件，進行刑事調查及紀律覆檢。"},{"pid":"54fa37da01dd3b24906149975d72047ca7f67bfe","tid":2286414,"uid":231583,"like":321,"dislike":1,"score":320,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T04:01:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a89e1f7cbf37957c9434e2349ac9b14eca5e13e8","tid":2286414,"uid":78243,"like":62,"dislike":1,"score":61,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T04:03:01.000Z","msg":"如果唔係偷返狗隊啲都未必俾人拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abca1ff342594a02dd52dacade3430d684175a33","tid":2286414,"uid":335434,"like":86,"dislike":2,"score":84,"quote":{"pid":"54fa37da01dd3b24906149975d72047ca7f67bfe","tid":2286414,"uid":231583,"like":321,"dislike":1,"score":320,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T04:01:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T04:04:47.000Z","msg":"隔離果部銳武都有承擔過佢 人地起碼都夠膽喺鏡頭前公